WEBVTT

00:00.016 --> 00:03.129
Why would I talk about
anything to you? You lie.

00:03.154 --> 00:04.805
<i>Previously on "Mistresses"... </i>

00:04.830 --> 00:06.707
Now, that's gonna be a problem.

00:06.732 --> 00:07.999
- [Smooches]
- Bye, love.

00:08.025 --> 00:09.008
Vivian: I'm telling you,

00:09.033 --> 00:10.377
apart from having a fatal disease,

00:10.402 --> 00:11.802
my life kicks ass.

00:11.837 --> 00:12.937
Alec: Why are you here alone?

00:12.972 --> 00:13.838
After a major procedure,

00:13.873 --> 00:15.594
why is there not someone here with you?

00:15.619 --> 00:17.456
Men like women with their hair down...

00:17.481 --> 00:20.015
at least your husband does.

00:20.040 --> 00:21.120
I thought we weren't talking.

00:21.145 --> 00:23.013
We're not.

00:31.754 --> 00:33.821
[Sighs]

00:39.015 --> 00:40.182
Hey.

00:40.207 --> 00:41.452
Hey.

00:42.572 --> 00:44.373
How long have you been staring at me?

00:44.398 --> 00:45.351
Oh...

00:45.417 --> 00:47.638
20-ish minutes, give or take.

00:47.663 --> 00:48.669
Oh.

00:48.694 --> 00:49.513
Is that weird?

00:49.538 --> 00:51.388
Oh... [Chuckles]

00:51.413 --> 00:53.017
We passed weird a long time ago.

00:53.311 --> 00:55.613
Then in that case, I'd like to uh...

00:55.648 --> 00:57.517
Just keep looking at you.

00:59.205 --> 01:00.873
- Ow!
- [Chuckles]

01:00.898 --> 01:01.920
What was that for?

01:01.944 --> 01:05.310
I just... I want to make sure
that this is actually happening.

01:05.334 --> 01:05.849
Is this real?

01:05.874 --> 01:07.608
Yes, and I'm pretty sure

01:07.633 --> 01:09.000
you're supposed to pinch yourself.

01:09.025 --> 01:10.419
Right. [Laughs]

01:10.444 --> 01:11.099
Sorry.

01:11.124 --> 01:14.360
Yeah, and, secondly, was that a, um...

01:14.385 --> 01:17.185
"This feels so good, I
can't believe it's happening"

01:17.210 --> 01:19.186
kind of pinch or...

01:19.406 --> 01:22.446
I can't believe what a
colossal mistake I've made?

01:22.471 --> 01:23.605
No, no, no, no, no.

01:23.630 --> 01:24.423
It was a positive pinch.

01:24.448 --> 01:25.728
- Yeah?
- So positive.

01:25.752 --> 01:26.885
[Chuckles]

01:27.647 --> 01:28.735
What about you?

01:28.760 --> 01:31.251
Are you having regrets or...

01:31.276 --> 01:32.321
Oh, yeah, this sucks.

01:32.346 --> 01:33.930
- Huh?
- Are you kidding?

01:33.955 --> 01:34.955
Oh!

01:35.023 --> 01:36.212
You're mean!

01:36.237 --> 01:37.204
What are you talking about?

01:37.229 --> 01:38.163
I can't see my face,

01:38.188 --> 01:39.665
but I feel like I'm grinning like an idiot.

01:39.690 --> 01:40.853
[Laughs] You are.

01:40.877 --> 01:43.516
- [Laughs]
- I grin like that?

01:43.541 --> 01:45.427
[Laughs] A little bit.

01:45.567 --> 01:47.432
I know what you mean, though.

01:47.457 --> 01:48.790
Hmm?

01:48.815 --> 01:52.717
Never in a million years
from where we started

01:53.249 --> 01:55.117
did I think we'd end up here.

01:58.137 --> 02:01.292
And where would you say we are?

02:04.800 --> 02:06.134
Happy.

02:06.746 --> 02:09.315
Mm. [Chuckles]

02:11.409 --> 02:13.042
Mmm.

